/i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ustamina01.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stamina01</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master</span><br>  Posts: 644<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/30/02 3:13:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11669.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.hempfiles.com/pictures/various/thumbnails/hash_nepal_ad_jpg.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Decisions, decisions</span><hr size=1> Scalia, Wow. You sure know your data.<br><br>I'd like to know your take on Gold Inlaid ulak as a Offhand? <p> <img src=http://www.hempfiles.com/pictures/fun/images/herbie.gif><b>Brother Stamina</b><br>60 Iksar Grandmaster<br>Cazic-Thule Server<br> <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=341210><u>Magelo Profile</u></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uscaliagluon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Scalia Gluon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 90<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/30/02 5:21:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11669.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Decisions, decisions</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  You sure know your data.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>Well, the actual &quot;data&quot; is easy to look up at Allakhazam and the math is of the vintage 4th grade variety :)<br><br><!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr